### ============================================================
### SportLink - Search Service - HTTP request samples
### ============================================================
### Service runs on http://localhost:8086
### Seeded by DataInitializer on startup:
###   FACILITIES:
###     sc-100  Tartu Sport Hall        BASKETBALL  Tartu
###     sc-101  Tallinn Football Arena  FOOTBALL    Tallinn
###     sc-200  Kalev Sport Center      BASKETBALL  Tallinn
###   USERS:
###     usr-100 Olena K. BASKETBALL INTERMEDIATE Tartu   rating 4.6
###     usr-101 Kirill M. FOOTBALL  ADVANCED     Tallinn rating 4.9
###   ACTIVITIES:
###     act-200 Sunday Pickup Basketball BASKETBALL OPEN Tartu
###     act-201 Friday Night Football    FOOTBALL   OPEN Tallinn
###
### Endpoints that work standalone (no peer service required):
###   * GET    /api/search
###   * GET    /api/search/users
###   * GET    /api/search/activities
###   * GET    /api/search/facilities         (without sportCenterId)
###   * GET    /api/search/index/{type}/{id}
###   * POST   /api/search/index
###   * DELETE /api/search/index/{type}/{id}
###
### Endpoints that need the Booking Service @ :8088:
###   * GET    /api/search/facilities?sportCenterId=...
### Returns 503 Service Unavailable when Booking is down.
### ============================================================


### ---------- 1. Swagger UI (open in browser) -----------------
GET http://localhost:8086/swagger-ui/index.html


### ---------- 2. OpenAPI spec (raw JSON) ---------------------
GET http://localhost:8086/v1/api-docs


### ============================================================
### CROSS-ENTITY SEARCH - GET /api/search
### ============================================================

### 3. All indexed entries (no filters)
GET http://localhost:8086/api/search


### 4. Free-text search - matches displayName and keywords
GET http://localhost:8086/api/search?q=basketball


### 5. Filter by entityType only
GET http://localhost:8086/api/search?entityType=FACILITY


### 6. Filter by entityType + sportType + location
GET http://localhost:8086/api/search?entityType=USER&sportType=BASKETBALL&location=Tartu


### 7. Filter by minRating (USER entries only have rating)
GET http://localhost:8086/api/search?entityType=USER&minRating=4.8


### ============================================================
### BOOKING-SERVICE INCOMING CALLS - GET /api/search
### These are the exact queries the Booking Service's SearchClient
### makes against this service.
### ============================================================

### 8. Same query the Booking Service makes internally for facility lookup
GET http://localhost:8086/api/search?entityType=FACILITY&sportType=BASKETBALL


### 9. With location filter
GET http://localhost:8086/api/search?entityType=FACILITY&sportType=BASKETBALL&location=Tartu


### 9b. With timeSlotId - routes to booking-aware facility search path
GET http://localhost:8086/api/search?entityType=FACILITY&sportType=BASKETBALL&timeSlotId=ts-300


### ============================================================
### USER SEARCH - GET /api/search/users
### Used by Matching Service to retrieve candidates.
### ============================================================

### 10. All users
GET http://localhost:8086/api/search/users


### 11. Filter by sport + skill level
GET http://localhost:8086/api/search/users?sportType=BASKETBALL&skillLevel=INTERMEDIATE


### 12. Filter by minimum rating
GET http://localhost:8086/api/search/users?userRatingScore=4.7


### ============================================================
### ACTIVITY SEARCH - GET /api/search/activities
### ============================================================

### 13. All activities
GET http://localhost:8086/api/search/activities


### 14. By title (substring, case-insensitive)
GET http://localhost:8086/api/search/activities?activityTitle=football


### 15. By status + sport
GET http://localhost:8086/api/search/activities?activityStatus=OPEN&sportType=BASKETBALL


### ============================================================
### FACILITY SEARCH - GET /api/search/facilities
### ============================================================

### 16. All facilities (no Booking Service call)
GET http://localhost:8086/api/search/facilities


### 17. By sport
GET http://localhost:8086/api/search/facilities?sportType=BASKETBALL


### 18. By sport + location
GET http://localhost:8086/api/search/facilities?sportType=BASKETBALL&location=Tartu


### 19. *** REAL INTEGRATION *** - by sportCenterId
###      triggers a synchronous call to Booking Service @ :8088.
###      Booking Service has seeded bookings for sc-100 and sc-101.
GET http://localhost:8086/api/search/facilities?sportCenterId=sc-100


### 20. sportCenterId for a center the Booking Service knows about
GET http://localhost:8086/api/search/facilities?sportCenterId=sc-101


### 21. sportCenterId for a center with no bookings -> empty result
GET http://localhost:8086/api/search/facilities?sportCenterId=sc-200


### ============================================================
### INDEX MAINTENANCE - GET / POST / DELETE
### ============================================================

### 22. Get a specific index entry
GET http://localhost:8086/api/search/index/FACILITY/sc-100


### 23. Upsert a brand-new index entry
POST http://localhost:8086/api/search/index
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "entityType": "FACILITY",
    "entityId":   "sc-300",
    "displayName":"New Volleyball Hall",
    "keywords":   ["volleyball", "tartu", "indoor"],
    "filters": {
        "sportType":    "VOLLEYBALL",
        "location":     "Tartu",
        "facilityName": "New Volleyball Hall"
    }
}


### 24. Upsert again with same entityType+entityId -> updates the existing row
POST http://localhost:8086/api/search/index
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "entityType": "FACILITY",
    "entityId":   "sc-300",
    "displayName":"New Volleyball & Badminton Hall",
    "keywords":   ["volleyball", "badminton", "tartu", "indoor"],
    "filters": {
        "sportType":    "VOLLEYBALL",
        "location":     "Tartu",
        "facilityName": "New Volleyball & Badminton Hall"
    }
}


### 25. Delete an index entry
DELETE http://localhost:8086/api/search/index/FACILITY/sc-300


### 26. Delete a non-existent entry  -> 404 Not Found
DELETE http://localhost:8086/api/search/index/FACILITY/does-not-exist


### 27. Get a non-existent entry  -> 404 Not Found
GET http://localhost:8086/api/search/index/USER/does-not-exist
